for each node
Balance level: -1,0,1
Balance index = RD - LD
4 rotations:
Left rotations: Node to the left above shifts down to the down left. Any nodes to the left from
the one getting rotated about get put to the right of the rotated node
Right rotations: Opposite of left, top right becomes right, previous right becomes left on rotated node
Left-right rotation (oh god): left-right leaning tree. Right node shifts to top right.Top right node of non-moved node
moves to right of the other moved node
Right-left rotation: the exact opposit